query:
SELECT buildPhase, typeOfResource, COUNT(*) as count, SUM(cost) as totalCost
FROM jobResources 
WHERE jobId = 330001
GROUP BY buildPhase, typeOfResource
ORDER BY buildPhase, typeOfResource;
